MODULE
     mnesia_session - Mnesia_Session

DESCRIPTION
     Mnesia is written in Erlang and  intended  to  be  used  for
     Erlang applications.

     The Mnesia_Session application enables access to the  Mnesia
     DBMS   from   foreign   programming  languages  (i.e.  other
     languages than  Erlang).  The  Mnesia_Session  interface  is
     defined  in  IDL (an Interface Definition Language standard-
     ized by OMG (the Object Management Group)).

